## 📊 Naval Warship OBB Dataset (4 Classes)

To support training and reproducibility, a **preprocessed and augmented sample dataset** has been provided. The dataset is annotated using **Oriented Bounding Boxes (OBB)** and contains four naval warship classes:

- Aircraft Carrier  
- Destroyer  
- Corvette  
- Submarine  

The dataset has been carefully curated from multiple sources and further enhanced using preprocessing and augmentation techniques including rotation, scaling, brightness adjustment, and orientation-based transformations. These augmentations improve model robustness under diverse maritime conditions such as varying angles, lighting, and background complexity.

Due to repository size limitations, a **sample version of the preprocessed and augmented dataset** has been uploaded to Kaggle.

📎 **Kaggle Dataset Link:**  https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/amanreddyj/naval-warship-yolo-obb-dataset


This dataset is provided to help users:

- Understand dataset structure  
- Train the model  
- Reproduce results  
- Perform further experimentation  

For full dataset access or additional information, please refer to the Kaggle link above.
